import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Stack,
  FormControl,
  FormErrorMessage,
  Input,
  Textarea,
  RadioGroup,
  Radio,
  Select,
  Button,
  Alert,
  AlertIcon,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";


export default function CreatePost() {
  return (
    <Box w={["100%", "90%", "80%", "70%"]} m="auto">
      <Stack spacing={3}>
        <FormControl>
          <RadioGroup>
            <Stack direction="row" spacing={3}>
              <Radio value="text">text post</Radio>
              <Radio value="link">link</Radio>
            </Stack>
          </RadioGroup>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <Input value={title} type></Input>
        </FormControl>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}
